    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours-level condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanically, the double VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rod bearing service is up to date. Finished in original Laguna Seca Blue with a flawless Nappa leather interior, this specimen retains its factory-fresh tactile feedback and high-revving linear power delivery. No leaks, no codes, just pure mechanical synchronicity.",
