    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that defines showroom excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, featuring a deep metallic finish that retains a mirror-like luster, entirely free of stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. The interior is a masterclass in preservation; the premium leather remains supple with zero bolster wear, and the cabin still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component and tactile switch operates with factory precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous schedule of preventative maintenance documented in a comprehensive service file. With a tight suspension and a seamless powertrain, this car drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. For the buyer who demands perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a flawless time capsule.",
